{"tid":1376713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一日冇更強武器其實真係冇辦法突破","createTime":"2019-07-28T11:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:38:12.000Z","uid":30274,"like":941,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4edf80462626dd3c9ce64d1c1e383340a96a6b","tid":1376713,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"班狗就好似試玩具咁成日有新野用<br />\n橡膠彈海綿布袋彈只係美化左個名，一樣大殺傷力<br />\n前線兄弟唔係金剛不壞身，傷一次已經可能短期再出唔到黎什至要長期訓醫院<br />\n<br />\n如果我地冇更好嘅武器或防具，個武力差別真係太大，遲早玩完<br />\n<br />\n20隻有槍我盾嘅狗已經可以封住500以上嘅人，只憑信念但冇高少少嘅武裝力量前線兄弟只會不斷犧牲"},{"pid":"becc9fcd93f18155933101af6f97b5b677a03fe1","tid":1376713,"uid":35484,"like":6,"dislike":323,"score":-317,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=55a38319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。"},{"pid":"168fbad273b0ff129e0d974fd367a1e532a565b1","tid":1376713,"uid":173849,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n三毛五毛見分化和理勇武失敗，依家spin去分化泛民、社工同劉細良，為保皇狗屌票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1376567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1376567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6187d4f465902e6f52fb95e2ec311aaa37d11cb","tid":1376713,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkg